name: Sarcophagus Marga Tengah
address: Unnamed Road, M7MP+9CJ, Kerta, Kec. Payangan, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80572, Indonesia
review 1:
Stopped here on a cycling tour.

Very interesting and beautifully maintained gardens.
review 2: it has Archeological value. Not a place to visit for vacation, but a place to visit to study new insight about the origin of Balinese people. These sarcophagus was lucky enough to be found and excavated. Many sarcophagus that was founded in this area never excavated or preserved.
review 3: Example of a well maintained archaeological site
